[size=3][center]
[size=2]Hello!

I'm sharing one of my main character RaceMenu preset & face Nif for Sculpt for anyone interested in using it as a base for their own Character or Custom Follower/NPC.
[/size]


[size=6]Jen Tai
[color=#6d9eeb]
DarkElf Vampire[/color]
[/size][/center][/size] [left][color=#ff0000][size=4]WARNING!!![/size][/color][color=#ff0000][size=4]MUST USE RaceMenu[/size][/color][size=4] by Expired
[color=#00ffff]([/color][color=#00ffff]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?[/color][color=#00ffff])[/color]  [b][u]How To Install[/u]:

Extract the contents of the ZIP file and copy to your Skyrim/data folder.

[u]How To Use[/u]:

At the character creation go to the presets tab of RaceMenu and load the
preset.
Also a Nif is supplied to be loaded from the Sculpt Tab.
 
[u]Required mods[/u]:

RaceMenu by [color=#00ffff]Expired[/color]
ApachiiSkyHair by [color=#00ffff]Apachii [/color]
 
[u]Body/Face textures used[/u]:

Mature skin texture and body for CBBE (v2 Beta)by [color=#00ffff]Maevan2[/color]
Brows by [color=#00ffff]Hvergelmir[/color]
Northborn Scars by [color=#00ffff]Northborn[/color]


[u]ENB used[/u]:

Kountervibe ENB Northern Light by [color=#00ffff]Kyokushinoyama[/color][/b]
[/size][/left]
